tool_description:
Yaware.TimeTracker is an automatic time tracking app that helps you and your team manage their time, be productive and achieve more.

Yaware.TimeTracker allows you to track time spent on projects, websites/software usage, manage resources, evaluate productivity and increase performance. All this without the need to start and stop a timer. The software allows to track software and Internet use, control overtime and flexitime, evaluate and reward achievements, take screenshots and snapshots.
